---

---

<section id="why-us" class="py-20 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-14">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-gray mb-4">
        Why Choose Smart Vend NC
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-light max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        We make vending effortless. Here's why businesses across the Triangle trust us.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Zero Cost -->
      <div class="group relative bg-off-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-muted/10 hover:border-primary/20 transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-8 w-12 h-1 bg-primary rounded-b-full"></div>
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-light rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-gray mb-3">Zero Cost to You</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-light leading-relaxed">We provide machines, installation, stocking, and maintenance completely free. You just provide the location.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Healthy Choices -->
      <div class="group relative bg-off-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-muted/10 hover:border-primary/20 transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-8 w-12 h-1 bg-primary rounded-b-full"></div>
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-light rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-gray mb-3">Healthy Snack Choices</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-light leading-relaxed">Curated selection of nutritious snacks, beverages, and fresh food that fuel productivity without the sugar crash.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Smart Machines -->
      <div class="group relative bg-off-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-muted/10 hover:border-primary/20 transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-8 w-12 h-1 bg-primary rounded-b-full"></div>
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-light rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.75 17L9 20l-1 1h8l-1-1-.75-3M3 13h18M5 17h14a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-gray mb-3">Modern & Smart Machines</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-light leading-relaxed">AI-powered inventory management ensures machines are always stocked with fresh, popular items. Cashless payments supported.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Local -->
      <div class="group relative bg-off-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-muted/10 hover:border-primary/20 transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-8 w-12 h-1 bg-primary rounded-b-full"></div>
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-light rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z"/><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-gray mb-3">Local & Family Operated</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-light leading-relaxed">Triangle-based team with same-day response for any issues. We're your neighbors, not a national call center.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
